posting_body: ["The Mezz at Fiddler's Green", '6440 Syracuse Way, Centennial, CO, 80111', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 22', 'OR Text', '22', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Get in tune with modern life.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 726 Sq.', 'Ft.', "The Mezz at Fiddler's Green is a new kind of community.", 'A place where modern features indoors are in perfect harmony with rugged nature scenery outdoors.', 'A place where your daily schedule is a melody of endless neighborhood conveniences.', 'A place where you can dial up or down the tempo between relaxation, invigoration, or vibation.', 'Features', '- Pendant Kitchen Lighting', '- In-home washer & dryer', '- Mountain or courtyard views', '- Luxury 1, 2, & 3 bedroom designs', '- Ceiling fans in living room and bedrooms', '- Key-Less Smart Locks', '- USB Equipped Electrical Outlets', 'Community Amenities', '- Smoke-Free Community', '- Rentable storage rooms', '- Online Payments Available', '- Garage & open surface parking', '- Indoor/outdoor flex entertainment patio', '- Bike repair station & bike racks', '- Cabanas, outdoor kitchen and fire features', '- 4-story design w/ elevator access', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', '$300 non-refundable pet fee for the first pet.', '$200 non-refundable pet fee for the second pet.', '$20 per month per pet.', 'Cats and dogs are accepted with no weight restriction.', 'No rodents, snakes, fish tanks or birds allowed.', 'A two pet maximum is permitted.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Hg1KVo2Atp']
